						               													<description>Gravellona 1944 &amp;egrave; la simulazione della battaglia di Gravellona Toce, svoltasi tra i partigiani della Repubblica dell'Ossola e i reparti repubblichini nel Settembre 1944.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Una simulazione tattica con diversi spunti interessanti!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Regole in italiano, pedine di gioco e tabelle!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game represents the battle between Italian partisans and republican fascists in September 1944. It is a tactical simulation with interesting ideas; units can do Actions by using Action Points, which are gained at the end of each turn and which must be planned carefully by the player. &amp;#10;Combat units are usually at platoon level or single veichle; each unit has a different capacity of fire, depending from the type of fire (Infantry, Tanks or Artillery) and the type of target (Infantry, Tanks and Veichles, Concrete targets). Morale tests and Hit results can apply on Fire, as well as during Mel&amp;egrave;e.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
